sequenceDiagram
    participant O as 订单服务
    participant DB1 as 订单库
    participant R as Outbox Relay
    participant MQ as RocketMQ
    participant C as 履约Consumer
    participant DB2 as 履约库
    participant J as 对账任务

    O->>DB1: 本地事务：订单置PAID + 插入Outbox(E1005,v7)
    DB1-->>O: COMMIT
    R->>DB1: 扫描未发送Outbox
    R->>MQ: 发送，Key=order_id，event_id=E1005
    MQ-->>R: ACK或结果未知
    R->>DB1: 成功则标记；未知则允许重发
    MQ->>C: 至少一次投递
    C->>DB2: 本地事务：Inbox(E1005)+状态机v7
    DB2-->>C: COMMIT
    C-->>MQ: ACK
    J->>DB1: 扫描已支付订单与Outbox
    J->>DB2: 核对履约状态
    J->>MQ: 缺失时按原event_id受控补发
